<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>PortFolioPH Realistic Roadmap</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #0d47a1;
      --blue-2: #1565c0;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --line: #cbd5e1;
      --ok: #16a34a;
      --warn: #ca8a04;
    }
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 28px;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #fff;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }
    .cover {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eef6ff 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .title { color: var(--blue); font-size: 30px; margin: 0; }
    .subtitle { color: var(--blue-2); font-size: 17px; margin: 4px 0 6px; }
    .meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin: 0; }

    h2 {
      margin: 18px 0 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--blue);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 8px;
      table-layout: fixed;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 8px;
      vertical-align: top;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    th {
      background: #eff6ff;
      color: #0b1e59;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .chip {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      background: #f0fdf4;
      color: #166534;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .chip.warn {
      border-color: #fde68a;
      background: #fffbeb;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    ul, ol { margin: 8px 0 8px 22px; }
    li { margin: 3px 0; }
    .note {
      margin-top: 14px;
      border: 1px dashed #94a3b8;
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="cover">
    <h1 class="title">PortFolioPH</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Offline/Online Portfolio Builder for Students</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>8-Sprint Agile Roadmap</strong> · 8 Weeks · 363 Total Hours</p>
    <p class="meta">Developer: Mark Leannie Gacutno (256h) · UX/QA: Tom Kyle B. Caballegan (≈55h) · Docs/Pres: Rex Bernard G. Gabor (≈52h)</p>
    <p class="meta">Platform: Flutter Android · Offline-first SQLite · Firebase sync · PDF export</p>
  </section>

  <h2>Workbook Sheet Format (Reference Applied)</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 26%">Sheet</th>
        <th style="width: 74%">Purpose</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>📋 Cover</td><td>Project summary & navigation</td></tr>
      <tr><td>📊 Dashboard</td><td>Sprint summary, hours budget, milestones</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 1</td><td>Core Setup & Architecture</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 2</td><td>Auth + Profile System</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 3</td><td>Projects CRUD + Gallery</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 4</td><td>Media Upload + Certificates</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 5</td><td>Achievements + Reflections</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 6</td><td>Resume Builder + PDF Export</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 7</td><td>Firebase Sync + Admin Panel</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🏃 Sprint 8</td><td>QA, Polish & APK Release</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🗺 Master Tracker</td><td>Single source of truth across all sprints</td></tr>
      <tr><td>📅 Class Schedule</td><td>8-week class mapping</td></tr>
      <tr><td>📦 Tech Stack</td><td>Package manifest + verification checklist</td></tr>
      <tr><td>📐 ERD</td><td>SQLite schema (10 tables)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>🗂 Flutter Scaffold</td><td>Complete folder/file structure</td></tr>
      <tr><td>✅ Day 1 Checklist</td><td>Sprint 1 kickoff checklist</td></tr>
      <tr><td>📈 Metrics</td><td>Success KPIs + progress tracking</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Roadmap Alignment Snapshot (External Reference → PortFolioPH)</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 30%">Theme</th>
        <th style="width: 48%">PortFolioPH Equivalent</th>
        <th style="width: 22%">Status</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Sprint 1 Infrastructure</td>
        <td>Core setup, routing, DB, theme</td>
        <td><span class="chip">✅ Completed</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Sprint 2 Core user flow</td>
        <td>Auth + profile setup</td>
        <td><span class="chip">✅ Completed</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Sprint 3 CRUD-heavy set</td>
        <td>Portfolio Projects CRUD + gallery</td>
        <td><span class="chip">✅ Completed</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Sprint 4 records/media</td>
        <td>Resume Certifications + certificate media upload</td>
        <td><span class="chip warn">🟡 In Progress</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Implemented Sprint 4 Slice</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Certification state management via <strong>CertificationProvider</strong>.</li>
    <li>Certificate image upload/delete service with local persistent file storage.</li>
    <li>Resume tab upgraded from placeholder to certification CRUD list with search.</li>
    <li>Add/Edit certification form with required field, URL, and date validation.</li>
    <li>Provider wiring added in app startup.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Next Recommended Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Add <strong>Education CRUD</strong> in Resume module.</li>
    <li>Add <strong>Work Experience CRUD</strong> in Resume module.</li>
    <li>Add timeline/section aggregation for complete Resume preview.</li>
    <li>Add widget tests for Resume certification flow.</li>
  </ol>

  <div class="note">
    This DOC is intentionally styled to follow the workbook-like roadmap format you referenced from
    <code>PortFolioPH_Realistic_Roadmap.xlsx</code>, while keeping the content aligned to the current
    implementation status of this repository.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
